---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon/components';
---

<Layout title="Tools" description="Free, open-source tools to hold power accountable and protect your rights.">
  <section class="hero-mini">
    <div class="container">
      <h1 data-en="Tools for the People" data-es="Herramientas para el Pueblo">Tools for the People</h1>
      <p data-en="Free, open-source tools to hold power accountable and protect your rights. Built by the community, for the community." data-es="Herramientas gratuitas y de código abierto para exigir rendición de cuentas y proteger tus derechos. Hechas por la comunidad, para la comunidad.">
        Free, open-source tools to hold power accountable and protect your rights.
        Built by the community, for the community.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="grid grid--2">
        <a href="/tools/eviction-tracker" class="card tool-card">
          <div class="tool-card__badge" data-en="Live Data" data-es="Datos en Vivo">Live Data</div>
          <div class="tool-card__icon"><Icon name="lucide:bar-chart-3" size={28} /></div>
          <h2 data-en="Denver Eviction Tracker" data-es="Rastreador de Desalojos de Denver">Denver Eviction Tracker</h2>
          <p data-en="Real-time dashboard of eviction filings scraped from Denver County Court records. See which landlords file the most evictions, which neighborhoods are hit hardest, and track trends over time." data-es="Panel en tiempo real de demandas de desalojo obtenidas de los registros del Tribunal del Condado de Denver. Mira qué propietarios presentan más desalojos, qué vecindarios son los más afectados y rastrea las tendencias a lo largo del tiempo.">
            Real-time dashboard of eviction filings scraped from Denver County Court records.
            See which landlords file the most evictions, which neighborhoods are hit hardest, and track trends over time.
          </p>
          <span class="tool-card__link">Launch Tool →</span>
        </a>

        <a href="/tools/rent-calculator" class="card tool-card">
          <div class="tool-card__badge" data-en="Interactive" data-es="Interactivo">Interactive</div>
          <div class="tool-card__icon"><Icon name="lucide:calculator" size={28} /></div>
          <h2 data-en="Rent Control Calculator" data-es="Calculadora de Control de Alquiler">Rent Control Calculator</h2>
          <p data-en="Enter your current rent and see how much you'd save under Denver For All's rent stabilization plan. Compare with and without vacancy decontrol. Generate a shareable graphic for social media." data-es="Ingresa tu alquiler actual y mira cuánto ahorrarías con el plan de estabilización de alquileres de Denver Para Todos. Compara con y sin descontrol de vacantes. Genera un gráfico compartible para redes sociales.">
            Enter your current rent and see how much you'd save under Denver For All's rent stabilization plan.
            Compare with and without vacancy decontrol. Generate a shareable graphic for social media.
          </p>
          <span class="tool-card__link">Launch Tool →</span>
        </a>

        <a href="/tools/campaign-finance" class="card tool-card">
          <div class="tool-card__badge" data-en="Follow the Money" data-es="Sigue el Dinero">Follow the Money</div>
          <div class="tool-card__icon"><Icon name="lucide:coins" size={28} /></div>
          <h2 data-en="Campaign Finance Tracker" data-es="Rastreador de Finanzas de Campaña">Campaign Finance Tracker</h2>
          <p data-en="Interactive visualization of campaign contributions to Denver City Council members and mayoral candidates. See which developers, landlords, and corporations fund which politicians - and how those politicians vote." data-es="Visualización interactiva de las contribuciones de campaña a los miembros del Concejo Municipal de Denver y candidatos a la alcaldía. Mira qué desarrolladores, propietarios y corporaciones financian a qué políticos - y cómo votan esos políticos.">
            Interactive visualization of campaign contributions to Denver City Council members and mayoral candidates.
            See which developers, landlords, and corporations fund which politicians - and how those politicians vote.
          </p>
          <span class="tool-card__link">Launch Tool →</span>
        </a>

        <a href="/tools/know-your-rights" class="card tool-card">
          <div class="tool-card__badge" data-en="AI-Powered" data-es="Impulsado por IA">AI-Powered</div>
          <div class="tool-card__icon"><Icon name="lucide:gavel" size={28} /></div>
          <h2 data-en="Know Your Rights" data-es="Conoce Tus Derechos">Know Your Rights</h2>
          <p data-en="AI-powered tenant rights assistant available 24/7 in English and Spanish. Ask questions about eviction, repairs, deposits, discrimination, and more. Chat or call - powered by real legal knowledge, not generic AI." data-es="Asistente de derechos del inquilino impulsado por IA disponible 24/7 en inglés y español. Haz preguntas sobre desalojos, reparaciones, depósitos, discriminación y más. Chat o llamada - impulsado por conocimiento legal real, no IA genérica.">
            AI-powered tenant rights assistant available 24/7 in English and Spanish.
            Ask questions about eviction, repairs, deposits, discrimination, and more.
            Chat or call - powered by real legal knowledge, not generic AI.
          </p>
          <span class="tool-card__link">Launch Tool →</span>
        </a>

        <a href="/tools/resistbot" class="card tool-card">
          <div class="tool-card__badge" data-en="Rapid Organizing" data-es="Organización Rápida">Rapid Organizing</div>
          <div class="tool-card__icon"><Icon name="lucide:send" size={28} /></div>
          <h2 data-en="Resistbot Campaigns" data-es="Campañas de Resistbot">Resistbot Campaigns</h2>
          <p data-en="Pre-written letter templates targeting every level of government. Copy a letter, text RESIST to 50409, and send it to your officials in under 2 minutes. Convert letters to petitions that anyone can sign." data-es="Plantillas de cartas pre-escritas dirigidas a todos los niveles de gobierno. Copia una carta, envía RESIST al 50409 y envíala a tus funcionarios en menos de 2 minutos. Convierte cartas en peticiones que cualquiera puede firmar.">
            Pre-written letter templates targeting every level of government.
            Copy a letter, text RESIST to 50409, and send it to your officials in under 2 minutes.
            Convert letters to petitions that anyone can sign.
          </p>
          <span class="tool-card__link">Launch Tool →</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .hero-mini {
    padding: 4rem 0 3rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-primary) 0%, var(--color-secondary) 100%);
    color: white;
  }
  .hero-mini h1 { color: white; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .hero-mini p { font-size: 1.15rem; opacity: 0.9; max-width: 700px; }

  .tool-card {
    display: block;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: inherit;
    position: relative;
  }

  .tool-card__badge {
    position: absolute;
    top: 1.5rem;
    right: 1.5rem;
    background: var(--color-primary-light);
    color: var(--color-primary-dark);
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 0.25rem 0.5rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
  }

  .tool-card__icon {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 56px;
    height: 56px;
    border-radius: 14px;
    background: var(--color-bg-alt);
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .tool-card h2 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .tool-card p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .tool-card__link {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }
</style>
